          "Actual Loss from the 1 default: Loan outstanding = ₹25 Cr; Recovery = ₹10 Cr; Actual Loss = ₹25 − ₹10 = ₹15 Cr.",
          "Actual loss (₹15 Cr) > EL (₹4.5 Cr) → this year was worse than average; provisions may be inadequate.",
