          { e: "💧", n: "Liquidity Stress Test", d: "Simulate sudden deposit outflows (e.g., 15% retail, 30% wholesale outflow in 5 days). Check if HQLA is sufficient. LCR stress test — compare to regulatory 100% minimum. Tests bank's contingency funding plan." },
          { e: "🌍", n: "Market Risk Stress Test", d: "Apply historical crisis scenarios to trading book: 2008 GFC, 2013 taper tantrum, 2020 COVID crash. Measure P&L impact. Determine if VaR model captures actual losses (backtesting). Stressed VaR computed for capital purposes." }
