          { e: "📋", n: "Special (Full) Endorsement", d: "Endorser signs and writes 'Pay to [Name]'. Named endorsee must endorse further. Most secure form of endorsement — restricts negotiation to specific person." },
          { e: "🔒", n: "Restrictive Endorsement", d: "'Pay [Name] only' or 'Not Negotiable' — prevents further transfer. 'Account payee only' crossing on cheque is a restrictive endorsement — must be credited only to named payee's account." }
