          { e: "👥", n: "CoC", d: "Committee of Creditors — all financial creditors. Decisions by 66% voting share. Operational creditors NOT members of CoC." },
          { e: "📋", n: "IRP/RP", d: "Interim Resolution Professional → Resolution Professional. Manages company affairs, invites resolution plans, ensures going-concern status." },
          { e: "💧", n: "Waterfall", d: "Liquidation priority: IBBI costs → secured creditors (workmen 24-month wages pari passu) → other employees → unsecured creditors → government dues → preference shareholders → equity." },
          { e: "🔑", n: "Section 29A", d: "Disqualifies promoters of NPAs (12+ months), wilful defaulters, and related parties from submitting resolution plans — prevents 'back-door entry'." },
          { e: "🏭", n: "PPIRP (MSMEs)", d: "Pre-Packaged Insolvency (2021 Amendment): only for MSME corporate debtors; default ≥ ₹10 lakh; debtor submits base plan with application; 120-day cap; Swiss Challenge for competing plans; debtor stays in management (debtor-in-possession). Sections 54A–54P." }
