          { e: "👥", n: "JLG/SHG", d: "Joint Liability Groups and Self-Help Groups are the dominant delivery models. JLG: 4-10 members, joint liability. SHG: 10-20 women, savings-led, bank-linked." },
          { e: "🔒", n: "No Collateral", d: "Microfinance loans must be collateral-free and without mandatory linked insurance (except credit insurance). Lenders cannot insist on savings deposit as pre-condition." }
