          { e: "🏢", n: "Institutional Arbitration", d: "ACI accredits arbitral institutions (DIAC, MCIA, ICADR). Institutional arbitration has pre-set rules, experienced arbitrators — more structured than ad hoc. Banks increasingly prefer institutional for large disputes." }
