          "PV of Terminal Value: ₹375 / (1.12)³ = ₹266.9 Cr.",
          "Enterprise Value = ₹17.86 + ₹17.54 + ₹17.79 + ₹266.9 = ₹320 Cr.",
          "Proposed price = ₹350 Cr > DCF value ₹320 Cr → 9% premium. Bank should probe: is there synergy value? Is growth assumption conservative? Price appears slightly high."
