          { e: "📐", n: "SOTP Valuation", d: "Sum-of-the-Parts: value each business segment separately using appropriate multiples → sum them → compare with market cap. If SOTP > market cap → conglomerate discount exists → restructuring unlocks value." },
          { e: "🏦", n: "Banking Impact", d: "Demergers affect bank's security structure (which entity holds the secured assets?). Bank must track: which company in restructuring holds the mortgaged property? Consent of secured creditors may be required." }
