          "NHAI Concession Agreement assigned to SPV: SPV has right to collect tolls for 30 years.",
          "EPC contract signed with construction firm (fixed-price, fixed-time — transfers completion risk).",
          "O&M contract signed with highway maintenance firm post-construction.",
          "Revenue escrow: ALL toll collections deposited in escrow account. Waterfall: O&M costs → debt service → DSRA top-up → equity returns.",
          "Result: conglomerate's balance sheet is protected. Banks lend based on projected toll cash flows, not conglomerate's credit."
