        problem: "A 200 MW solar project has base case DSCR of 1.42×. Perform sensitivity on three variables: PLF (base 22%), electricity tariff (base ₹3.50/unit), and O&M cost (base ₹8 Cr/year). Impact of each 5% adverse change on DSCR:",
