          "Political/regulatory risk: Concession agreement with Ministry of Power + termination payment provisions → partially allocated to government.",
          "Environment risk: EIA clearance obtained; fly ash management plan agreed → bank CPs include these clearances.",
          "Force majeure: Property All Risk insurance + Business Interruption insurance for 24 months → allocated to insurer."
