          { e: "🏷️", n: "ET4: Clients/Products/Business Practices", d: "Losses from unintentional or negligent failure to meet professional obligations: mis-selling (ULIP, structured products), market manipulation, antitrust violations, KYC failures. Often large — regulatory fines." },
          { e: "🏢", n: "ET5: Damage to Physical Assets", d: "Losses from natural disasters or other events: fire in branch, floods damaging data centre, earthquake, vandalism, terrorism. Typically covered by property insurance." },
          { e: "💻", n: "ET6 & ET7", d: "ET6: Business Disruption & System Failures — CBS downtime, network outage, Y2K, power failure. ET7: Execution, Delivery & Process Management — trade settlement errors, data entry mistakes, contract management failures, vendor disputes." }
