        opts: ["An operational loss that almost breaches the reporting threshold but falls just under it", "An event or situation that could have caused an operational loss but did not, due to chance or timely intervention", "A risk that is identified in RCSA but has never caused an actual loss in the industry", "A regulatory near-violation where the bank came close to breaching a limit but stayed within it"],
