          { e: "🦠", n: "Pandemic/Cyber BCM", d: "COVID-19 triggered pandemic BCP: remote working, split teams, rotational staffing. Cyber BCM: backup networks isolated from compromised systems, air-gapped backups, playbooks for ransomware. RBI Circular on BCM (2020) updated for cyber threats." }
